channel.title: Epic SSBB Music
channel.description:
I was playing Super Smash Bros. Brawl and noticed that some of the songs was pretty awesome. So I youtube'd some of the songs.
I have two favorites already :
Shin Onigashima - Ice climber level http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=45JS6hA0Mcc&feature=channel_page
Gourmet Race - Kirby level http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5KKW3MT-8PU&feature=channel_page
Also, the person uploading theese songs have all of them (I think). Just check the: "More From: DeoxysPrime" on the side.
